tool_description: Since Zumper.com doesn't provide an API, this API will help you to retrieve data from it.
name: Zumper.com Scraper
title: Zumper.com Scraper

api_list.name: properties Details
api_list.description: Get more details for a property
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://zumper-com-scraper.p.rapidapi.com/properties/details"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "zumper-com-scraper.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
